  "text": "Unstructured N-or C-terminus segments can be problematic for protein analysis or molecular simulation. Using PP, this type of segment was observed in half of the protein structures found in Protein Data Bank [CITATION_1] . We thus included a new assignment method in the web server. A PU is considered unstructured if it is isolated at the first cutting event and never thereafter.",
